                The checkLastName() function validates the last name input in addEmployee.html. It returns:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>False:</strong> If the last name contains non-alphabetic characters, triggering an error alert.</li>
                <li><strong>True:</strong> If the last name consists only of alphabetic characters, allowing form submission.</li>
